{"tid":1543110,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"認真諗翻轉頭 得老衲酒店全劇最慘係桑切斯","createTime":"2019-09-05T05:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T06:50:14.000Z","uid":152123,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9d1f1cc30c11306cd64ab88425eff976a750212","tid":1543110,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"讀書時期 撞正心理變態殺人狂<br />\n名譽掃地 慘遭欺凌到差啲吞槍自殺<br />\n<br />\n美羅當自己係連兵都不如 白食白住提款機<br />\n為咗追燦星就痴埋嚟住<br />\n為咗追英秀 冇問過佢批准就帶仔翻去自己屋企瞓<br />\n但明明間屋主人係桑切斯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n中間撞過鬼 差啲要同隻女鬼冥婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU見佢有錢當佢水魚<br />\n<br />\n難得溝到個靚女高質女朋友 又長期Long D只能facetime<br />\n打算求婚 埋門一腳女朋友都炒車死撚埋 客死異鄉中國上海<br />\n<br />\n長期都冇朋友咁款 得自己一丁友整pizza<br />\n唯一最老死嘅具燦星 最後因為情傷搬走埋去紐約<br />\n美羅英秀結婚搬走<br />\n結果得翻桑切斯一個人on99係韓國唔知做乜<br />\n人生所有配點都落曬去財富上面 但佢又唔貪圖名利<br />\n<br />\n宣佈全劇最坎坷一定係桑切斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他怨鬼都可以行埋一邊"},{"pid":"f9d97411369e1bec4b6133ab83abe63c6097da80","tid":1543110,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3